{"lastModified":1764335300471,"uri":"c::7580644256::vessel::8cda3750-3fe4-11f0-8eb4-9330118c2ec5","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Corsica, French Riviera & Monaco, Italy - North (mainland), Italy - Sardinia, Provence Coast & Marseille\n\nBLUE EYES is a Princess 95 motor yacht, launched in 2009 and fully refitted in 2024. She is now available for charter for the first time and offers a luxurious experience for up to 8 guests in 4 well-appointed staterooms. A dedicated crew of 5 ensures top-tier service and a relaxed onboard atmosphere.\nThis yacht stands out for her spacious outdoor areas, including a large sundeck with loungers, a bar, and a shaded lounge area, an aft deck that offers an inviting space for relaxed lunches or dinners, while sunbeds at the bow provide the perfect spot to enjoy cocktails at sunset with stunning views.\nIndoors, guests will find a light-filled saloon with Mediterranean-inspired décor, a generous dining area, and modern amenities throughout. BLUE EYES is also equipped with a wide range of water toys, including 2 jet skis and more with a swimming platform—perfect for guests seeking both relaxation and adventure.","blueprint":{"name":"BLUE EYES","images":["/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel::8cda3750-3fe4-11f0-8eb4-9330118c2ec5::assets::27fc8cc0-421e-11f0-8247-ebc53c8255ce/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel::8cda3750-3fe4-11f0-8eb4-9330118c2ec5::assets::27fab800-421e-11f0-8247-ebc53c8255ce/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel::8cda3750-3fe4-11f0-8eb4-9330118c2ec5::assets::6d3c3600-421e-11f0-b701-3f6f1251e499/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel::8cda3750-3fe4-11f0-8eb4-9330118c2ec5::assets::27fa1bc0-421e-11f0-8247-ebc53c8255ce/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel::8cda3750-3fe4-11f0-8eb4-9330118c2ec5::assets::27fa42d0-421e-11f0-8246-ebc53c8255ce/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel: